djondb php driver
==================


Compilation
===========

Just execute the script compile.sh and it will do the work for you, like this:

chmod +x compile.sh
./compile.sh

If you cannot execute the compile script, the steps you will need to do are as follows:


phpize
./configure --enable-djonwrapper
make


Install
=======

Install the libraries in the php folder using this command:

sudo make install

Add the module descriptor file to the php ini folder:

cp etc/djonwrapper.ini /etc/php5/mods-available

Activate the module creating a symbolic link using:

ln -s /etc/php5/mods-available/djonwrapper.ini /etc/php5/conf.d/djonwrapper.ini


Help
====

If you need help please visit http://djondb.com, there you will find the documentation, support
pages, etc.
